    "instructions": Combatible for use with Turn: A Slice of Life, Supernatural Roleplaying Game of Shapeshifters in Small Towns, from Beau Jágr Sheldon/Thoughty. Turn is a game about shapeshifters living quietly in a small town, navigating the push and pull between their human and beast natures.

Roll20 Character Sheet

•	Human and Beast archetype tab with separate abilities, background text, and goals for 9 human and 9 beast archetypes 
•	Each sheet self-populates once an archetype is selected from a drop-down menu
•	Habit and Instinct stat blocks with Powers and Struggles roll buttons
•	Dedicated Turn Die button with dedicated result cards and a stress reminder
•	Human Stress and Beast Stress tracks
•	Town Exposure and Animal Group Exposure tracks with positive and negative radial buttons

How to Use
Select your Human and Beast archetypes from the dropdown menus on each page. Your stat values will populate automatically. Enter your character information, then use the Roll buttons next to each Habit or Instinct to make Powers or Struggles rolls — results appear as illustrated cards in the chat window.

